title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the Edit Data Set dialog.
SR: Details: The output parameter should be displayed in the Edit Data Set dialog. Steps to reproduce: 1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 2. The query result will be stored in the output parameter as an object.
